631
00:45:09,334 --> 00:45:13,755
"Gray Wolf" je gladan.

632
00:45:15,299 --> 00:45:17,843
Vaše žene će saznati da ste
izginuli...-"Greyhound" pratnji.

633
00:45:17,926 --> 00:45:21,138
