01:17:04,750 --> 01:17:07,544
Poruka za most. Pošalji.
-Poruka za most, razumem.

1023
01:17:07,628 --> 01:17:10,297
Komodor javlja još pet minuta
do promene kursa, Kapetane.

1024
01:17:10,380 --> 01:17:12,549
